Name: Ninja Frog
About the game: Ninja Frog is a cute platformer game. It has cute graphics and simple gameplay. There are 7 different types of traps and a nice character in the game. The game levels go from easy to difficult, but all levels are easily passed. ▪ 50 Unique level ▪ 100 Achievements Credits Graphics: Pixel Adventure from Pixel Frog Music: Free Music Pack Vol. 1 from Final Gate Studios
